LINEAGE:
This repo is the successor to the Perfect Pitch Deck Figma template by Steve
Butler at https://www.figma.com/community/file/1430528713594279249. The slide
structure, sales-psychology sequencing, and copy guidance carry over from that
template. If you remix the original Figma file, follow the terms set by Figma
Community on that file's page.

THIRD-PARTY NOTICES:

This kit redistributes / embeds the following open-source components. Their
copyright notices and license terms are preserved in the relevant files.

  Reveal.js — Copyright (C) 2011-2026 Hakim El Hattab and contributors
  https://github.com/hakimel/reveal.js — MIT License
  Used at runtime (loaded via CDN) AND verbatim in `assets/speaker-view.html`,
  which is a self-hosted copy of reveal.js's speaker-view template.

  intl-tel-input — Copyright (C) Jack O'Connor and contributors
  https://github.com/jackocnr/intl-tel-input — MIT License
  Used at runtime (loaded via CDN) on slide 23's phone-number field.

  staticrypt — Copyright (C) Robin Moisson
  https://github.com/robinmoisson/staticrypt — MIT License
  Used as a build-time dependency to gate the deck behind a passphrase.
  The kit's `staticrypt-template.html` is a customised version of staticrypt's
  default password template.

  Fonts (Inter, Mona Sans, JetBrains Mono)
  Loaded from Google Fonts under the SIL Open Font License v1.1.

